casebody.data:
Paul Eugene NASEMAN, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Jason EGGLESTON, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157325
COA: 339479 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 2, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the January 26, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
